{"tid":680201,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA] 覺唔覺得Steve Kerr係最幸運嘅人？","createTime":"2018-05-27T04:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T05:31:04.000Z","uid":63568,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"95e2c567880ed8007fd2ceceb2d48e26dce02b1f","tid":680201,"uid":63568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:54:38.000Z","msg":"論做球員<br />\n係公牛 可以痴到MJ神級球員<br />\n然後三年霸拎champ<br />\n係馬刺 可以幸運到 第一年拎到冠軍<br />\n然後下年去第二隊 隔年返馬刺又拎多次冠軍<br />\n<br />\n論做教練<br />\n係公牛 跟過Phil Jackson世界級教練<br />\n係馬刺 跟過Pop 又係世界級教練<br />\n呢兩個教練 如果話係NBA史上最佳都唔過份<br />\n然後入到勇士 呢隊勇士已經有前任教練打好根基<br />\n有一班優秀既制服組幫你pick左一班好既球員<br />\n第一年係勇士教 已經可以闖入Final<br />\n仲要對住殘陣騎士拎championship<br />\n<br />\n隔年自己開季受傷教唔到波<br />\n但居然有個助教幫自己開季24連勝<br />\n然後73勝破紀錄<br />\n<br />\n再下一年居然可以有KD 又係名人堂級球員<br />\n<br />\n呢個幸運程度 真係無人能及"},{"pid":"1a920ce6b26f854034769361c2cc698ee4bedcfe","tid":680201,"uid":63568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:56:13.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家討論"},{"pid":"3181c9fcf09cead2350b510fbf2d7a5cacb5e14e","tid":680201,"uid":152520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"Lue 好似幸運啲"},{"pid":"9d0ccb3d4b6823d4ae1d1eaa671065b5013b8785","tid":680201,"uid":54025,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"同施丹一樣，死好運"},{"pid":"9461cbb13e7562bd267075b1f3131948f62bb2a3","tid":680201,"uid":29886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"Mike Brown <br />\nBryon Scoot <br />\nAlvin Gentry <br />\n呢堆冇料又呃到飯食幸運d"},{"pid":"3d83ac365ad16ed356fe1f12ae4cd7bbda036a48","tid":680201,"uid":63568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9461cbb13e7562bd267075b1f3131948f62bb2a3","tid":680201,"uid":29886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"Mike Brown <br />\nBryon Scoot <br />\nAlvin Gentry <br />\n呢堆冇料又呃到飯食幸運d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:02:32.000Z"